NEW SMALL BUSINESS! 

@demisdelights_bakery 

As some of you may have seen over the last week I have taken the brave step to start my own business baking cakes from home! 

This is going to be a side occupation to my full time job but I have always loved baking and can’t wait to share my creations with you all.

I would love it if my lovely foodie friends who I have made along the way from running this blog would follow my new page @demisdelights_bakery and give it some love, whether you are far or near it would be much appreciated! 

I am currently awaiting my registration from the council which means I cannot start trading until after the 22nd March!

alt: Photo by Mom.Wife.Nurse on February 27, 2022. May be an image of dessert.
caption:
Brownies bez šećera ,brašna i jaja!! 
Recept:
➡️ 210 g umaka od jabuka
➡️125 g kikiriki maslaca
➡️ 80 g  kakao
➡️ 2 čk vanila ekstrakt 
➡️50 - 70 g javorovog sirupa
➡️100 g tamne čokolade 
 
Frostinging:

➡️ 100 g sirnog namaza 
➡️3 Kašike javorovog sirupa 

➡️Sastojke za brownies sve zajedno dobro umjesajte, stavite u manju  vatrostalnu posudu ,i pecite na 180 C° oko 20 min
Kada se ispeče dobro ohladiti (2-3 sata u hladnjaku)

➡️pomiješati sirni namaz i javorov sirup ,preliti po brownies i uživajte 🍹
